code: @Override public List<ServiceDefinition> getServices(String name) {     return discoveryClient.getInstances(name).stream().map(si -> {         return DefaultServiceDefinition.builder().withName(si.getServiceId()).withHost(si.getHost()).withPort(si.getPort()).withId(name).withMeta(si.getMetadata()).build().     }).collect(Collectors.toList()). }
